---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../../consts';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import FooterEng from '../../components/en-components/FooterEng.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Privacy Policy"
description="Learn how your personal data is processed and protected on this website."
 />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="datenschutz-section">
        <h1 class="subpage-heading">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Protecting your personal data is very important to me. I therefore process your data exclusively in accordance with the applicable legal provisions (GDPR, TKG 2003).</p>

        <h2>Contacting Me</h2>
        <p>If you contact me via the form on this website or via email, the data you provide will be stored for six months for the purpose of processing the request and in case of follow-up questions. This data will not be shared without your consent.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website uses technically necessary cookies to ensure functionality. Additionally, cookies for analytical purposes are only set with your consent (see below: Google Analytics).</p>

        <h2>Server Logs</h2>
        <p>The hosting provider of this website automatically collects and stores information in so-called server log files, which your browser automatically transmits. This includes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Operating system used</li>
          <li>Referrer URL</li>
          <li>Hostname of the accessing device</li>
          <li>Time of server request</li>
          <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
        <p>This website uses Google Analytics, a web analytics service provided by Google Ireland Limited ("Google"), Gordon House, Barrow Street, Dublin 4, Ireland. Usage is based on your consent in accordance with Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR.</p>

        <p>Google Analytics uses cookies that enable analysis of your use of the website. The information generated by the cookie is generally transferred to a Google server in the USA and stored there. However, your IP address is anonymized before transmission ("IP anonymization"). This means the data cannot be directly linked to you as a person.</p>

        <p>Google will use this information to evaluate your use of the website, compile reports on website activity, and provide other services related to website and internet usage.</p>

        <p>You can prevent the storage of cookies by adjusting your browser settings accordingly. You can also revoke your consent at any time via the cookie banner or disable tracking using the following browser add-on:</p>

        <p><a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a></p>

        <p>For more information on Googleâ€™s data processing, please visit:  
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a>
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, rectification, erasure, restriction, data portability, and objection. If you believe your data is being processed unlawfully, you can file a complaint with the data protection authority.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, you can contact me at:<br>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:jasmin.kitzbichler@gmail.com">jasmin.kitzbichler@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <FooterEng />
  </body>
</html>

<style lang="scss">

    .datenschutz-section{
        width: 720px;
        max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
        margin: auto;


        p, h2, li{
            text-align: center;
            display: block;
        }
    }
</style>